Package: crunchdev
Type: Package
Title: Development tools for Crunch's R packages
Description: Provides a number of tools to ease development of Crunch's R 
    packages. Including RStudio addins that make testing quicker and more
    flexible within RStudio.
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2017-08-09
